-- 02_join_transactions_with_stores.sql
```sql
SELECT
    t.transaction_id,
    t.customer_id,
    t.amount,
    COALESCE(s.city, 'Unknown') AS city,
    c.channel
FROM transactions t
LEFT JOIN stores s ON t.store_id = s.store_id
LEFT JOIN customer_primary_channel c ON t.customer_id = c.customer_id
```

-- 03_revenue_by_channel_city.sql
```sql
WITH customer_primary_channel AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT ON (customer_id)
        customer_id,
        channel
    FROM customer_channels
    ORDER BY customer_id, attributed_at DESC
),
transactions_enriched AS (
    SELECT
        t.transaction_id,
        t.customer_id,
        t.amount,
        COALESCE(s.city, 'Unknown') AS city,
        COALESCE(c.channel, 'Unattributed') AS channel
    FROM transactions t
    LEFT JOIN stores s ON t.store_id = s.store_id
    LEFT JOIN customer_primary_channel c ON t.customer_id = c.customer_id
)
SELECT
    channel,
    city,
    SUM(amount) AS total_revenue,
    COUNT(transaction_id) AS transaction_count,
    COUNT(DISTINCT customer_id) AS unique_customers
FROM transactions_enriched
GROUP BY channel, city
ORDER BY total_revenue DESC;
